76
00:03:53,420 --> 00:03:56,825
Whenever a ship passes near the land,

77
00:03:56,825 --> 00:03:59,830
it is called a sail past or sail by.

78
00:03:59,830 --> 00:04:04,846
Normally, such big ships sail 
at a distance of 7-8 km from the shore

79
00:04:04,846 --> 00:04:06,719
