00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:04,443
and saying that he couldn't go back.

356
00:17:12,974 --> 00:17:16,637
Despite all of this, Captain Schettino did not go back.

357
00:17:16,637 --> 00:17:22,185
This is why people started calling him Captain Coward later.

358
00:17:22,185 --> 00:17:26,416
On one hand, some brave crew members 
and the Italian Coast Guard team

359
00:17:26,416 --> 00:17:29,358
kept helping people all night.

360
00:17:29,358 --> 00:17:32,246
Schettino sat at a safe distance and watched it play out.

361
00:17:32,246 --> 00:17:36,143
When the sun rose the next morning, 
and the ship could be seen properly,

362
00:17:36,143 --> 00:17:41,346
people realised the magnitude of the incident.

363
00:17:41,346 --> 00:17:43,694
Look at these photos taken in the morning.

